com.waughrn2.ca4006.NextUpdate

Class Car

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.waughrn2.ca4006.NextUpdate.Car

  • public class Car
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstraction of a Car as it is used by all parts of the simulation. Note that the only information that is necessary about a car is when it is sent from the simulator and when it departs from the parkingLot.
